    "created_at": "2017-04-11T13:58:07Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-04-11T14:03:03Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The point is that `LaysTerrain` is specifically designed to only place tiles within the `Building` footprint.  This PR makes it so that tiles can bleed outside the building footprint, which then fundamentally changes the behaviour of the trait and makes the behaviour inconsistent between PickAny and normal templates.\r\n\r\nThe example you have given above illustrates that the concrete actor is being spawned in the wrong position relative to the infantry.  You need to fix *that* instead, so that your blue rectangle can cover the same cells as your black rectangle."
  },
